Interface IEvaluator<DATA,DATA_VARIABLE>

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractASTVisitor, ComplexEvalVisitor
public interface IEvaluator<DATA,DATA_VARIABLE>

Interface for java.lang.Object based evaluation engines (typicaly implemented as IASTVisitors). For example the ComplexEvalVisitor class uses the Complex class data type.

See Also:
IASTVisitor, ComplexEvalVisitor
